Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.72,0:00:03.23,Italics_top,F,0,0,0,,{"I want to read books."}"Mình muốn đọc sách"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.57,0:00:06.41,Italics_top,F,0,0,0,,{For the girl who began a new life \Nas Main in another world—}Cô gái bắt đầu cuộc sống mới ở thế giới khác Myne--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.41,0:00:09.23,Italics_top,F,0,0,0,,{a world where books and paper \Nare prohibitively expensive—}nơi mà sách và giấy vô cùng đắt đỏ,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.23,0:00:10.75,Italics_top,F,0,0,0,,{that was her biggest wish.}đã mong ước như vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.16,0:00:14.61,Italics_top,F,0,0,0,,{If she couldn't get any, she'd \Nhave to make them herself.}Nếu không thể mua được thì tự viết.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.90,0:00:16.83,Italics_top,F,0,0,0,,{Having come to that resolution,}Và để có thể làm thế,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.83,0:00:19.58,Italics_top,F,0,0,0,,{she took the first step toward \Nmaking her own paper...}cô bé đã đi bước đầu tiên là tạo ra giấy...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.56,0:00:46.77,Title,Title Card,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,1)\pos(320.667,63)}{Ascendance of a Bookworm}Sự thống trị của mọt sách
