Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.01,0:02:01.01,Ep Title,Ep Title,0,0,0,,{\pos(500.667,247.667)}Chương 3: \N Lễ hội mùa đông
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.18,0:02:06.35,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{Two months after I became Main,}Hai tháng sau khi tôi trở thành Myne,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.66,0:02:10.24,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{Winter with a capital W took \Nover the town I live in.}mùa đông đã đến trên thành phố W nơi tôi sống.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.66,0:02:22.08,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Why is it so dark in the middle of the day?}Trưa mà sao tối vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.65,0:02:24.82,Default,T,0,0,0,,{What do you expect? There's a blizzard outside.}Tại trời đang có bão mà, chịu thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.31,0:02:34.15,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{As getting snowed in is very common, \Npeople work at home over the winter.}Vì mọi người đã quen với nó nên vẫn làm việc trong nhà.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.15,0:02:35.58,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{Mainly handiwork.}Chủ yếu là làm thủ công.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.11,0:02:37.97,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{Turi makes baskets,}Turi làm túi,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.37,0:02:40.47,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{while Mom stitches clothes.}còn mẹ thì may quần áo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.47,0:02:44.35,Default,E,0,0,0,,{Main, you should stop goofing \Noff and make some baskets, too.}Myne, con cũng đừng ngồi đó nữa mà ra phụ đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.35,0:02:47.10,Default,E,0,0,0,,{Show her how to do it, Turi.}Turi, chỉ em cách làm đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.52,0:02:48.68,Default,T,0,0,0,,{Sure.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.34,0:02:53.84,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Sorry, I already know what I'm making.}Em biết cách làm lâu rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.11,0:03:03.35,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I'm gonna make pseudo-papyrus with this.}Mình sẽ làm giấy giả cói bây giờ.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.92,0:03:05.61,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{Before it started snowing,}Trước khi tuyết rơi,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.61,0:03:09.75,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{I had Turi and the other kids gather \Na thick-stemmed plant for me.}mình, Turi cùng mấy bạn hàng xóm đã đi lấy ít thân cây.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.24,0:03:12.71,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Ancient Egypt is dead! \NLong live Ancient Egypt!}Ai Cập cổ đại là số 1! Hoan hô!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.65,0:03:18.36,Default,M,0,0,0,,{How do I extract the fiber, though?}Nhưng làm cách nào để lấy được sơ ra nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.63,0:03:26.50,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Wow. Turi, how do you make this?}Tuyệt quá, chị làm thế nào vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.50,0:03:30.14,Default,T,0,0,0,,{You skin it, wash it in running \Nwater, and then let it dry.}Em lột vỏ, rửa bằng nước và phơi khô.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.43,0:03:31.82,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I see.}Hiểu rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.30,0:03:33.70,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Thanks!}Cảm ơn!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.29,0:03:35.25,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Okay!}Ừm!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.44,0:03:46.90,Default,M,0,0,0,,Turi...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.51,0:03:49.82,Default,T,0,0,0,,{Try peeling along the fiber now.}Sau đó lột sơ ra đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.85,0:03:57.37,Default,M,0,0,0,,Turi...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.67,0:04:00.03,Default,M,0,0,0,,{All done!}Xong rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.03,0:04:03.11,Default,M,0,0,0,,{What's wrong, Turi?}Sao thế Turi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.81,0:04:08.55,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{And so, the table was set.}Thế là phần chuẩn bị đã xong.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.55,0:04:15.82,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Now if I just weave these together, \NI should have my pseudo-papyrus!}Giờ thì đan mấy thứ này lại là có giấy
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.81,0:04:17.73,day,Sign,0,0,0,,{Day 1}Ngày 1
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.73,0:04:19.82,day,Sign,0,0,0,,{Day 2}Ngày 2
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.82,0:04:21.74,day,Sign,0,0,0,,{Day 3}Ngày 3
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.74,0:04:26.46,Default,T,0,0,0,,{You've been at it for three days.}Nè, đã 3 ngày rồi đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.46,0:04:28.12,Default,T,0,0,0,,{What are you trying to make?}Em đang làm gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.53,0:04:32.61,Default,T,0,0,0,,{Main?}Myne?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.75,0:04:35.25,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Forget it!}Dẹp đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.25,0:04:39.39,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I give up! You win this war, Ancient Egypt!}Bỏ cuộc! Các người đã thắng, Ai Cập cổ đại!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.39,0:04:41.34,Default,E,0,0,0,,{Keep it down.}Ồn ào quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.34,0:04:44.13,Default,E,0,0,0,,{And make some baskets instead \Nof playing with that grass.}Nếu rảnh rỗi thế thì con đan giỏ đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.43,0:04:46.29,Default,M,0,0,0,,{'Kay...}Vâng...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.29,0:04:48.77,Default,T,0,0,0,,{I'll teach you how to do it.}Chị sẽ chỉ em cách làm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.23,0:04:52.05,Default,M,0,0,0,,{It's okay. I know how.}Em biết cách làm rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.26,0:04:55.43,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{Back when I was Urano,}Hồi còn là Urano,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.43,0:05:00.26,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{my mom made me help make baskets \Nout of newspaper leaflets.}mẹ bắt mình làm giỏ từ giấy báo cũ mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.29,0:05:06.27,Default,E,0,0,0,,{That's impressive, Main!}Tuyệt quá nhỉ, Myne!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.93,0:05:09.31,Default,T,0,0,0,,{Why are you so much better at it?}Tại sao em ấy lại làm đẹp hơn?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.86,0:05:12.61,Default,T,0,0,0,,{I'm supposed to be the big sis...}Con là chị mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.82,0:05:18.92,Default,M,0,0,0,,{N-No, this is, uh...}K-Không phải, đây là...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.92,0:05:22.16,Default,T,0,0,0,,{You want to be an apprentice \Nseamstress, right?}Turi muốn trở thành một thợ may mà nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.93,0:05:26.92,Default,T,0,0,0,,{Then you'll need to learn how \Nto weave before your baptism.}Vậy thì con nên học cách đan giỏ trước lễ rửa tội đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.92,0:05:29.90,Default,T,0,0,0,,{Come, I'll teach you.}Nào, mẹ chỉ cho.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.71,0:05:31.96,Default,T,0,0,0,,{Yay!}Vâng!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.27,0:05:37.77,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{Nice save, Mom!}Mẹ tuyệt quá!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.10,0:05:40.46,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{Turi turns seven in the summer.}Turi sẽ lên 7 tuổi hè này.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.46,0:05:44.88,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{In this world, once a kid \Nturns seven and is baptized,}Trong thế giới này, khi đứa trẻ lên 7 và rửa tội,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.88,0:05:46.78,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{they begin life as an apprentice.}chúng sẽ bắt đầu cuộc sống học việc.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.24,0:05:50.57,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{To become an apprentice, you \Nneed an adult's referral.}Để trở thành học việc thì cần có người giới thiệu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.57,0:05:55.03,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{As such, most people end up in the \Nsame line of work as their parents.}Nên hầu hết mọi người đều làm công việc giống ba mẹ.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.47,0:05:57.79,Default,E,0,0,0,,{You should learn how to weave too, Main.}Con cũng nên học cách đan đi, Myne.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.79,0:05:59.66,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I'll pass.}Con không học đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.99,0:06:01.11,Default,E,0,0,0,,{No, you won't.}Không được.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.11,0:06:05.16,Default,E,0,0,0,,{You need to know how to make attractive \Nyet practical clothes for your family.}Con cần phải biết cách may những bộ quần áo đẹp cho gia đình.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.16,0:06:07.77,Default,E,0,0,0,,{Or else, you won't be a refined lady.}Nếu không sẽ không trở nên xinh đẹp đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.22,0:06:09.39,Default,M,0,0,0,,{"Refined"?}Xinh đẹp?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.39,0:06:13.40,Default,E,0,0,0,,{Right. A refined lady must \Nknow how to cook and sew.}Phải, muốn làm phụ nữ đẹp phải biết may vá và nấu nướng.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.40,0:06:16.14,Default,M,0,0,0,,{It's not like I want to be a seamstress.}Nhưng con không muốn làm thợ may.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.14,0:06:18.96,Default,T,0,0,0,,{Do you wanna be an apprentice craftsman?}Em có muốn trở thành thợ thủ công không?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.31,0:06:21.41,Default,T,0,0,0,,{You do make a mean basket, after all.}Lúc nãy em làm giỏ đẹp lắm mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.68,0:06:23.29,Default,M,0,0,0,,{No, no!}Không, không!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.29,0:06:24.79,Default,T,0,0,0,,{What will you do, then?}Vậy em muốn làm gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.51,0:06:28.33,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Of course...}Dĩ nhiên...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.02,0:06:31.69,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I'll make books!}Em sẽ làm sách!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.48,0:06:35.10,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Ancient Egypt didn't help.}Nhưng Ai Cập cổ đại lại không giúp mình...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.96,0:06:37.21,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Then, naturally,}Vậy thì tiếp theo,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.94,0:06:40.82,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I'll turn to Mesopotamia next!}mình sẽ chuyển sang Mesopotamia!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.05,0:06:45.02,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Okay, I'm making clay tablets in the spring.}Rồi, hè mình sẽ chuyển sang làm đất sét.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.98,0:06:52.42,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Morning.}Chào buổi sáng.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.42,0:06:53.83,Default,E,0,0,0,,{Good morning, Main.}Chào con, Myne.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.04,0:06:57.89,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Huh? Where are Dad and Turi?}Ủa? Ba với Turi đâu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.34,0:07:00.31,Default,E,0,0,0,,{They went to pick parues.}Họ đi chọn parues rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.98,0:07:02.57,Default,M,0,0,0,,Parues?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.59,0:07:28.13,Default,G,0,0,0,,{Turi, you okay?}Turi, ổn chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.13,0:07:31.12,Default,T,0,0,0,,{Yeah. I think I'm almost done.}Vâng, còn xíu nữa thôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.99,0:07:35.64,Default,T,0,0,0,,{We're back!}Về rồi đây!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.58,0:07:38.78,Default,M,0,0,0,,{So this is the parue fruit?}Ra đây là trái parue.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.78,0:07:41.02,Default,T,0,0,0,,{Main, hold the bowl for me.}Myne, mang tô lại đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.33,0:07:42.28,Default,M,0,0,0,,{'Kay.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.98,0:07:54.49,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Wow, that's a sweet scent!}A, thơm quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.30,0:07:56.57,Default,T,0,0,0,,{Wanna drink some?}Uống thử không?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.57,0:07:57.39,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Yeah!}Ừm!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.83,0:08:07.25,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{It's like rich coconut milk!}Giống sữa dừa quá!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.19,0:08:10.60,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{Such a blissful taste!}Vị của hạnh phúc.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.39,0:08:15.26,Default,M,0,0,0,,{That was amazing.}Ngon quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.26,0:08:20.51,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Turi, why are your hands all red?}Turi, tay chị đỏ quá. Sao vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.87,0:08:23.52,Default,T,0,0,0,,{It always happens when you pick parues.}Lúc nào lấy parue cũng vậy đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.01,0:08:28.77,Default,T,0,0,0,,{You can't do it unless you warm \Nup the branches with your hands.}Em phải lấy nó bằng hơi ấm của bàn tay mới được.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.10,0:08:31.97,Default,M,0,0,0,,{With your bare hands? In this cold?}Bằng tay? Trời lạnh vậy mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.97,0:08:34.64,Default,T,0,0,0,,{You'd catch a cold right away.}Nếu là em thì cảm ngay đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.64,0:08:37.19,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Can't you do it in the afternoon?}Để chiều làm không được hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.19,0:08:39.78,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Wouldn't that make them easier to thaw?}Lúc đó thì trời ấm lên một chút mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.78,0:08:41.03,Default,T,0,0,0,,{Absolutely not.}Không được.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.35,0:08:44.91,Default,T,0,0,0,,{Parue fruits can only be \Npicked in the morning.}Trái parue chỉ lấy được vào buổi sáng đến trưa thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.34,0:08:47.96,Default,T,0,0,0,,{When exposed to sunlight, \Nthe tree grows rapidly,}Khi gặp ánh nắng mặt trời, cây sẽ lớn lên,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.96,0:08:51.09,Default,T,0,0,0,,{sends its fruit flying far \Naway, and disappears.}và phát tán trái của nó đi xa rồi biến mất.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.66,0:08:52.93,Default,M,0,0,0,,{It disappears?}Biến mất?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.80,0:08:56.43,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Sounds like one bizarre tree.}Một cái cây kì lạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.75,0:09:02.59,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{Once Dad finished separating \Nthe parues' flesh, oil, and pulp,}Sau khi ba làm xong việc tách dầu, thịt và bột parue,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.59,0:09:04.43,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{he left for his night shift at work.}ông ấy đi làm ca đêm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.68,0:09:18.33,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Looks like soy pulp.}Giống bột đậu nành nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.58,0:09:25.21,Default,T,0,0,0,,{No, Main! That's bird feed!}Myne, đó là mồi câu chim mà!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.13,0:09:33.58,Default,M,0,0,0,,{This is actually pretty edible!}Cái này... ăn được đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.04,0:09:36.57,Default,R,0,0,0,,{Good evening!}Chào buổi tối.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.08,0:09:40.58,Default,R,0,0,0,,{Could you spare us some parue \Npulp in exchange for eggs?}Cậu đổi ít bột parue cho bọn tớ lấy trứng nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.96,0:09:43.22,Default,R,0,0,0,,{We're running low on bird feed.}Bọn tớ không đủ mồi câu chim.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.49,0:09:45.59,Default,T,0,0,0,,{Sure. Hang on.}Được thôi, chờ chút.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.54,0:09:54.22,Default,L,0,0,0,,{There are a bunch of boys in my family,\Nso food is starting to be a problem.}Nhà bọn mình nhiều anh em nên không đủ thức ăn cho lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.22,0:09:57.12,Default,M,0,0,0,,{If you're hungry, do you wanna try this?}Nếu đói thì ăn thử cái này nè.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.12,0:10:00.27,Default,L,0,0,0,,{Huh? Who'd eat bird feed?!}Hả? Ai lại ăn mồi câu chim chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.62,0:10:08.51,Default,L,0,0,0,,{It's good.}Ngon vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.51,0:10:11.74,Default,M,0,0,0,,{There's a way to make it taste even better.}Có cách để làm nó ngon hơn đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.50,0:10:25.51,Default,M,0,0,0,,{You flip it once bubbles \Nform on the surface.}Khi nào thấy có bong bóng nổ là lật mặt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.55,0:10:36.56,Default,L,0,0,0,,{Man, I can't watch. Let me do it.}Nguy hiểm quá, để tớ.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.20,0:10:40.53,Default,L,0,0,0,,{One, two...}Hai ba...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.61,0:10:48.63,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Ta-dah!}Xong!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.63,0:10:51.49,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Your simple paruecake is ready to eat!}Bánh parue đã có thể ăn!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.19,0:11:09.27,Default,L,0,0,0,,{This is great.}Ngon quá!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.64,0:11:10.99,Default,R,0,0,0,,{Good! So good!}Ngon! Quá ngon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.29,0:11:13.07,Default,E,0,0,0,,{This is fantastic, Main.}Tuyệt thật đó, Myne.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.07,0:11:14.87,Default,T,0,0,0,,{Where did you learn to make this?}Em học làm món này ở đâu vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.87,0:11:18.87,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Well, you got your hands all \Nred to get these for us.}Khó khăn lắm chị mới lấy được trái parue về.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.25,0:11:23.71,Default,M,0,0,0,,{And this way, we can eat all of it.}Làm thế này thì có thể xài được hết trái parue nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.06,0:11:29.09,Default,T,0,0,0,,{Yeah! Thanks, Main!}Ừm, cảm ơn em, Myne!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.61,0:11:32.12,Default,L,0,0,0,,{Damn, you're cool.}Cậu tuyệt thật.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.12,0:11:36.07,Default,M,0,0,0,,{These are easy to make, and filling.}Bánh này làm dễ mà ăn no nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.07,0:11:38.20,Default,L,0,0,0,,{I'll be there for you next \Ntime you need anything.}Lần tới bọn này sẽ giúp nữa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.75,0:11:44.81,Default,L,0,0,0,,{You're weak and frail, so let me help you,}Myne đâu có sức khỏe đâu, nên tớ sẽ giúp.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.81,0:11:47.02,Default,L,0,0,0,,{as thanks for the paruecake.}Để cảm ơn vì bánh parue.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.02,0:11:54.06,Eyecatch_an4,Gu,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,1000)}{Ascendance of a\N Bookworm}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.07,0:12:00.03,Eyecatch_an6,Gu,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,1)}{Ascendance of a\N Bookworm}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.03,0:12:03.91,Default,G,0,0,0,,{Wow, Main made these?}Myne làm à?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.91,0:12:06.10,Default,E,0,0,0,,{They're paruecakes, apparently.}Bánh parue.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.10,0:12:07.51,Default,G,0,0,0,,{Let's have a bite.}Ăn thử xem nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.32,0:12:11.46,Default,G,0,0,0,,{Yummy!}Ngon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.46,0:12:14.54,Default,T,0,0,0,,{Hard to believe they're \Nmade from the pulp, right?}Thật khó tin khi làm nó từ bột parue nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.39,0:12:20.18,Default,T,0,0,0,,{But first the Simple All-In-One \NShampoo, and now this...}Nhưng bánh này và dầu gội đa năng hôm trước...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.18,0:12:22.42,Default,T,0,0,0,,{Where did she learn to make all this?}Em ấy học ở đâu không biết?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.16,0:12:27.93,Default,E,0,0,0,,{She did make a really elaborate \Nbasket all by herself, too.}Hôm bữa con bé còn đan giỏ đẹp lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.93,0:12:31.18,Default,T,0,0,0,,{Hasn't she been really strange lately?}Gần đây em ấy thật kì lạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.18,0:12:33.82,Default,G,0,0,0,,{Who cares if she's acting strange?}Ai quan tâm chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.82,0:12:37.72,Default,G,0,0,0,,{She kept having fevers and \Ncould've died anytime, you know?}Ngày xưa con bé có thể lên cơn sốt và mất bất cứ lúc nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.48,0:12:42.24,Default,G,0,0,0,,{I'm happy just seeing how active she is now.}Ba thật vui khi thấy hiện tại nó đang rất hạnh phúc.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.02,0:12:46.45,Default,E,0,0,0,,{You're right.}Phải nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.45,0:12:47.34,Default,T,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.50,0:12:53.19,Default,M,0,0,0,,{My slate pencil is gone!}Hết chì viết bảng rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.63,0:12:55.97,Default,T,0,0,0,,{Oh, big deal.}Tưởng gì...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.97,0:12:57.46,Default,M,0,0,0,,{It }{\i1}{is}{\i0}{ a big deal!}Quan trọng lắm đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.77,0:12:59.97,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Dad, take me to the gate!}Ba, dẫn con đến cổng!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.32,0:13:02.20,Default,G,0,0,0,,{Why the gate?}Làm gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.67,0:13:05.56,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I need to get more slate\Npencils from Mister Otto.}Con cần lấy thêm chì từ chú Otto.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.56,0:13:08.97,Default,M,0,0,0,,{And I'll have him teach me some \Nmore letters while I'm at it.}Và nhờ chú ấy dạy viết chữ nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.12,0:13:14.35,Default,G,0,0,0,,{Do you like Otto that much?}Con thích chú Otto thế à?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.35,0:13:16.10,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Yeah! I love him!}Vâng! Con thích chú ấy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.78,0:13:23.33,Default,G,0,0,0,,{Not until the spring.}Ở nhà cho đến mùa xuân.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.50,0:13:28.25,Default,G,0,0,0,,{Not until the spring!}Ở nhà cho đến mùa xuân!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.42,0:13:31.58,Default,G,0,0,0,,{You'll catch a fever if you go outside!}Con sẽ bị sốt đấy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.58,0:13:34.76,Default,G,0,0,0,,{You're not taking one step out of \Nthe house until the spring! Got that?!}Cấm không được ra khỏi nhà cho đến mùa xuân! Hiểu chưa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.16,0:13:36.43,Default,T,0,0,0,,{Dad...}Ba...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.04,0:13:39.50,Default,E,0,0,0,,{What am I going to do with him?}Thiệt tình, ông chồng phiền phức.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.76,0:13:45.64,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Stupid overbearing dad!}Ba là đồ ngốc!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.50,0:13:52.00,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{However, the very next day had \Nperfect parue-picking weather,}Ngày hôm sau là một ngày hoàn hảo để lấy parue,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.26,0:13:55.38,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{so Mom and Turi headed out to the forest,}nên mẹ và Turi sẽ vào rừng.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.66,0:13:58.91,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{and Dad had to take me to the gate anyway.}Còn ba thì dẫn mình đến cổng.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.90,0:14:05.71,Default,M,0,0,0,,{We're in }{\i1}{Snow Country}{\i0}{.}Thành phố tuyết.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.42,0:14:08.56,Default,G,0,0,0,,{Main.}Myne.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.56,0:14:10.65,Default,M,0,0,0,,{What is it, Dad?}Gì vậy ba?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.62,0:14:15.93,Default,G,0,0,0,,{Otto's a married man, okay?}Otto đã cưới rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.15,0:14:17.10,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{Urk.}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.88,0:14:23.32,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Uh... What about it?}Thì sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.72,0:14:27.17,Default,G,0,0,0,,{That guy's mind is filled \Nwith nothing but his wife.}Tâm trí của tên đó chỉ toàn dành cho vợ mình.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.80,0:14:33.60,Default,M,0,0,0,,{So you're saying he's a \Ndevoted, loving husband,}Tức là ba đang nói chú Otto yêu vợ,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.60,0:14:36.68,Default,M,0,0,0,,{and an all-round great guy?}và là một người đàn ông tuyệt vời?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.37,0:14:40.80,Default,G,0,0,0,,{No.}Không.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.56,0:14:49.13,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{He's such a pain!}Phiền phức vãi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.57,0:14:52.11,Default,O,0,0,0,,{Main!}Myne!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.51,0:14:53.87,Default,O,0,0,0,,{It's been a while.}Đã lâu không gặp!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.87,0:14:56.50,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Long time no see, Mister Otto.}Lâu không gặp, chú Otto.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.48,0:15:00.71,Default,G,0,0,0,,{Eva will come pick her up once \Nshe's done picking parues.}Eva sẽ đến đón con bé sau khi lấy parue xong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.06,0:15:02.99,Default,G,0,0,0,,{Take care of Main until then.}Chăm sóc Myne hộ tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.45,0:15:05.55,Default,O,0,0,0,,{But, uh, I...}À nhưng mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.55,0:15:07.11,Default,G,0,0,0,,{You get it, don't you?}Cậu hiểu chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.38,0:15:12.50,Default,G,0,0,0,,{Don't you dare let her catch \Na cold like last time.}Đừng có để con bé bị cảm như hôm bữa đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.00,0:15:18.86,Default,O,0,0,0,,{Welp.}Thiệt tình.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.86,0:15:22.72,Default,O,0,0,0,,{I was about to do the accounts \Nand draw up next term's budget.}Chú đang chuẩn bị lập ngân sách cho sang năm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.81,0:15:27.77,Default,M,0,0,0,,{He started sulking when \NI spoke highly of you.}Mỗi khi khen chú Otto là ba cháu lại giận dỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.77,0:15:29.68,Default,O,0,0,0,,{Yikes.}Chà...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.28,0:15:33.23,Default,O,0,0,0,,{But still, I'm happy to see you again.}Nhưng chú cũng vui khi được gặp lại Myne.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.74,0:15:38.14,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{After that, Otto gave me a fresh slate pencil}Sau đó chú Otto cho mình thêm chì viết,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.14,0:15:40.60,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{and taught me some more letters.}và chỉ mình thêm mấy chữ mới.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.65,0:15:44.07,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I think I've learned a fair few now.}Nhớ được kha khá rồi đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.87,0:15:54.33,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Mister Otto.}Chú Otto.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.19,0:15:57.20,Default,M,0,0,0,,{This part is incorrect.}Phần này sai rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.80,0:15:59.32,Default,M,0,0,0,,{So is this.}Chỗ này nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.90,0:16:02.95,Default,O,0,0,0,,{You can do calculations?}Cháu tính toán được hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.95,0:16:04.77,Default,O,0,0,0,,{But you can't read, right?}Nhưng lại không đọc được?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.77,0:16:06.57,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I don't know the alphabet,}Cháu không biết đọc chữ,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.57,0:16:09.56,Default,M,0,0,0,,{but Mom taught me the numbers before.}nhưng mẹ có chỉ cháu về số rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.03,0:16:12.97,Flashback,M,0,0,0,,{Mom! What's that on that plank?}Mẹ, cái kia là gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.29,0:16:18.86,Flashback,E,0,0,0,,{Oh, it shows the price, so you know \Nhow much you can buy something for.}À, là giá đó. Khi mua gì đó thì cần nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.17,0:16:34.76,Default,O,0,0,0,,{Main, I'm going to swallow my pride and ask.}Myne, chú cần cháu giúp.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.11,0:16:37.26,Default,O,0,0,0,,{Could you help me out here?}Cháu giúp chú chỗ này nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.25,0:16:45.79,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Sure thing!}Vâng!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.79,0:16:49.26,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I'll do it if you supply slate pencils for \Nme and teach me the alphabet.} Nếu chú cho cháu thêm chì viết bảng và dạy cháu chữ.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.85,0:16:54.60,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I'm not the kind of girl who \Nworks for no compensation.}Phải có phần thưởng cháu mới làm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.25,0:17:00.11,Default,O,0,0,0,,{You're so amusing.}Myne thú vị thật đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.54,0:17:03.11,Default,O,0,0,0,,{Do you really only want\Nslate pencils, though?}Nhưng cháu chỉ cần chì viết bảng thôi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.22,0:17:06.50,Default,M,0,0,0,,{It runs out in no time.}Nó sẽ hết nhanh lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.96,0:17:09.76,Default,O,0,0,0,,{I see. In that case,}Vậy à, thế thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.97,0:17:12.76,Default,O,0,0,0,,{we have a deal.}đây là thỏa thuận.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.37,0:17:23.56,Default,O,0,0,0,,{Can I ask you to get right to \Nworking on these calculations?}Cháu có thể tính toán hộ chú phần này không?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.40,0:17:26.03,Default,O,0,0,0,,{Here's your calculator.}Đây là máy tính.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.03,0:17:29.07,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I don't need it. I don't \Nknow how to use it, anyway.}Cháu không biết cách xài nó nhưng mà không sao.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.95,0:17:31.79,Default,O,0,0,0,,{How will you do it, then?}Vậy tính thế nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.79,0:17:34.27,Default,M,0,0,0,,{All I need is the slate.}Bảng này là đủ.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.62,0:17:43.41,Default,O,0,0,0,,{Wow.}Ồ!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.41,0:17:47.15,Default,O,0,0,0,,{I can't believe you did such complicated \Ncalculations without using a calculator.}Không thể tin là cháu có thể\N tính toán mà không cần máy tính.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.11,0:17:50.56,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{Crap. Did I do too much?}Mình làm quá hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.59,0:17:54.48,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I'm glad to be of help.}Thật may vì cháu làm được việc.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.81,0:17:57.17,Default,O,0,0,0,,{You really were. Thank you.}Cháu cứu chú lần này rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.46,0:17:59.44,Default,T,0,0,0,,{Main!}Myne!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.44,0:18:00.63,Default,E,0,0,0,,{Time to go home!}Về thôi con!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.63,0:18:03.14,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Oh, Turi! Mom!}A, Turi! Mẹ!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.69,0:18:07.83,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{And then came one snowy day after another.}Và những ngày tuyết rơi lại tiếp tục.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.45,0:18:10.43,Default,E,0,0,0,,{Okay, all done!}Xong rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.43,0:18:16.92,Default,E,0,0,0,,{That's what you'll wear to \Nyour baptism. Isn't it pretty?}Bộ đồ con sẽ mặc trong lễ rửa tội đó, đẹp không?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.92,0:18:17.66,Default,T,0,0,0,,{Yeah!}Ừm!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.33,0:18:20.30,Default,T,0,0,0,,{Thank you, Mom!}Cảm ơn mẹ!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.59,0:18:27.84,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{Oh, so we use the free time over \Nthe winter to prepare for summer.}Vậy là dùng thời gian rảnh mùa đông \Nđể chuẩn bị cho mùa hè à?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.84,0:18:33.65,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Turi, what about your hair?}Turi, tóc chị thì sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.65,0:18:37.84,Default,T,0,0,0,,{I'll pick some flowers and \Nuse them as a hair ornament.}Chị định dùng vài bông hoa và đeo lên trang trí tóc.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.84,0:18:39.69,Default,M,0,0,0,,{That's not enough!}Như vậy không đủ!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.25,0:18:43.02,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I'll make you look way prettier than that!}Em sẽ làm chị dễ thương hơn nữa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.42,0:18:46.01,Default,M,0,0,0,,{If we don't have hair accessories, \NI can just make some!}Nếu không có đồ trang trí tóc thì mình có thể tự làm!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.27,0:18:51.04,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{I'll show off the lacework skills I got from\Nall those hours at mommy crafting classes!}Mình muốn thể hiện tất cả khả năng\N sau hàng giờ học tập lớp thủ công.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.37,0:18:58.60,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{Wait, this world doesn't \Nhave the crochet hook yet!}Nhưng thế giới này không có kim móc!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.57,0:19:01.91,Default,M,0,0,0,,{That means...}Thế thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.34,0:19:08.67,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Dad.}Ba.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.41,0:19:12.66,Default,G,0,0,0,,{What do you want?}Gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.66,0:19:15.91,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{Yikes. He's still sulking.}Vẫn đang hờn...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.52,0:19:22.68,Default,M,0,0,0,,{You see, I need a favor from you.}Con có việc muốn nhờ...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.99,0:19:25.18,Default,G,0,0,0,,{A favor?}Việc?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.18,0:19:26.49,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.49,0:19:30.45,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Can you make me a needle with \Na hook to stitch thread?}Ba có thể làm cho con một cây kim móc không?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.01,0:19:33.42,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Pretty please?}Con muốn có...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.42,0:19:37.40,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Pretty please?}Con muốn có...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.85,0:19:41.18,Default,G,0,0,0,,{I'll give it a shot!}Để ta làm thử!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.18,0:19:43.13,Default,M,0,0,0,,{You're the best, Dad!}Ba là số một!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.01,0:19:50.50,Default,G,0,0,0,,{Will this do?}Thế này hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.50,0:19:52.71,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Can you make it thinner?}Có thể mỏng hơn không?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.71,0:19:54.80,Default,G,0,0,0,,{Of course. You got it.}Rồi, để ba!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.04,0:19:55.62,Default,T,0,0,0,,{Dad's in a better mood now.}Ba đang vui lại rồi nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.62,0:19:57.97,Default,E,0,0,0,,{Yeah. That's great.}Ừm, may quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.98,0:20:00.35,Default,G,0,0,0,,{How's this?}Thế này thì sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.38,0:20:05.62,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I love you, Dad!}Con yêu ba nhất!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.00,0:20:11.63,Default,G,0,0,0,,{Victory is mine, Otto.}Tôi thắng rồi đấy, Otto.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.89,0:20:14.40,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Mom, can I have some waste thread?}Mẹ, cho con mấy thứ bỏ đi này nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.40,0:20:17.30,Default,E,0,0,0,,{Sure, but what will you do with it?}Được... Mà con định làm gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.52,0:20:29.99,Default,M,0,0,0,,{There!}Xong rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.99,0:20:31.80,Default,T,0,0,0,,{Isn't it too small?}Nó nhỏ xíu vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.80,0:20:34.53,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I'll make a bunch of these \Nand put them together.}Em sẽ làm thật nhiều và may chúng lại.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.43,0:20:39.74,Default,E,0,0,0,,{Let me try.}Để mẹ thử nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.66,0:20:44.93,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{Wow. A refined seamstress in action.}Ồ, không hổ là thợ may chuyên nghiệp.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.93,0:20:48.76,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{Then I had Dad make the hairpin part too,}Mình đã bảo ba cùng làm nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.76,0:20:50.69,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{and the hair ornament was complete!}Và đồ trang trí tóc đã hoàn thành.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.12,0:20:54.33,Default,M,0,0,0,,{It's done.}Xong rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.05,0:20:58.85,Default,E,0,0,0,,{That looks great.}Trông tuyệt quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.85,0:21:00.45,Default,M,0,0,0,,{You're so pretty, Turi.}Dễ thương quá, Turi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.21,0:21:04.71,Default,T,0,0,0,,{I do?}Vậy sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.29,0:21:09.06,Default,T,0,0,0,,{This really is great!}Thứ này tuyệt quá!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.06,0:21:13.60,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I wanted to repay you for helping \Nme extract the fiber from the grass.}Em muốn cảm ơn chị vụ tách sơ hôm bữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.53,0:21:16.55,Default,T,0,0,0,,{Thanks, Main.}Cảm ơn Myne.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.88,0:21:19.53,Default,T,0,0,0,,{This makes me really happy.}Chị vui lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.53,0:21:21.56,Default,G,0,0,0,,{Dad's really happy, too!}Ba cũng vui nữa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.92,0:21:24.85,Default,G,0,0,0,,{Main's a kind girl who cares for her sister.}Myne là một đứa em út biết quan tâm đến chị.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.85,0:21:28.61,Default,G,0,0,0,,{And Turi's grown into a lovely big sis, too!}Và Turi đã trở thành một người chị xinh đẹp!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.61,0:21:31.07,Default,G,0,0,0,,{You girls are my pride and joy!}Hai đứa là niềm tự hào của ba!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.03,0:23:11.53,Next_Chapter,Title,0,0,0,,{Next Chapter\N}{\fs24}{Forests and Clay Tablets}Tập sau: Rừng và đất sét
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.84,0:23:14.35,Default,F,0,0,0,,{You have a very nice and caring father.}Con có một người cha tuyệt vời nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.35,0:23:16.98,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Yeah, but he's way too clingy.}Nhưng ông ấy hơi bám dính...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.36,0:23:21.01,Default,F,0,0,0,,{By the way, when are you \Ngoing to start making paper?}Cơ mà con định khi nào mới làm giấy?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.01,0:23:23.66,Default,F,0,0,0,,{You haven't done anything you said you'd do.}Con vẫn chưa làm được gì đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.66,0:23:26.45,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Hey, I did make pseudo-papyrus.}Con có làm nè.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.45,0:23:28.62,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Though it was a dead end.}Nhưng thất bại.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.62,0:23:31.54,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I'm gonna make clay tablets for sure next!}Lần tới sẽ là đất sét!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.54,0:23:33.88,Default,F,0,0,0,,{Clay is hardly paper.}Nó có phải là giấy đâu.
